WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.150 --> 00:00:09.460
QTO — turn drawings into a schedule of quantities, right in your browser.

2
00:00:09.760 --> 00:00:17.630
Click “Start measuring” — no registration, everything runs locally.

3
00:00:17.930 --> 00:00:31.120
Open the PDF tab and upload a drawing — or try the sample.

4
00:00:31.420 --> 00:00:45.010
Set the scale: the app detects it automatically — just apply it.

5
00:00:45.310 --> 00:01:08.380
Measure wall lengths: click start and end points, then “Done”.

6
00:01:08.680 --> 00:01:32.950
Outline rooms with the Area tool — finishes are generated automatically.

7
00:01:33.250 --> 00:01:56.680
Count doors, windows and fixtures — every click is tallied.

8
00:01:56.980 --> 00:02:20.330
Report tab: summary, self-check and a one-click Excel export.
